---
/**
 * Visual and conceptual showcase of agentic workflows and Anthropic research
 * Highlights modular, node-based agent flows, neural maps, and references
 */
---

<section id="agentic" class="cyber-section" style="background: var(--color-cyber-surface);">
  <div class="cyber-container">
    <h2 class="cyber-section-title">Agentic Workflows & Anthropic Research</h2>
    <div
      class="description"
      style="max-width:780px;margin:0 auto 2.5rem auto;font-size:1.2rem;color:var(--color-cyber-text-dim);"
    >
      Modulární architektury, orchestrace více AI agentů, a bezpečnost srozumitelná v obrazech.<br />
      Agentic workflows umožňují autonomní plánování, reasoning, exekuci a spolupráci více AI systémů.
      <br /><b>Anthropic</b> zkoumá transparentnost neuronových aktivací, <b>vědecký přístup k interpretaci modelů</b> a
      bezpečnostní rámce s důrazem na <b>koordinační vzory agentů</b>.
    </div>

    <div
      class="showcasegrid"
      style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(320px,1fr));gap:2rem;align-items:start;"
    >
      <!-- 1. Modular Agentic Workflow (Flowchart style) -->
      <div class="showcase-item fade-in" tabindex="0" aria-label="Visual: Modular agentic workflow chart">
        <figure
          style="background:var(--color-cyber-bg);padding:1rem;border-radius:1rem;border:1px solid var(--color-cyber-border);"
        >
          <img
            src={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}/assets/images/ai-hero.svg`}
            alt="Agentic workflow modular chart"
            loading="lazy"
            style="width:100%;max-width:350px;margin:auto;display:block;"
          />
          <figcaption style="text-align:center;margin-top:0.5rem;font-size:.96rem;">
            <b>Modulární agentic workflow</b><br />
            <span style="color:var(--color-cyber-blue)">Sensing → Reasoning → Planning → Coordination → Acting</span>
          </figcaption>
        </figure>
      </div>

      <!-- 2. Anthropic Monosemanticity/Neural Map -->
      <div class="showcase-item fade-in" tabindex="0" aria-label="Anthropic research visual example">
        <figure
          style="background:var(--color-cyber-bg);padding:1rem;border-radius:1rem;border:1px solid var(--color-cyber-border);"
        >
          <img
            src="https://cdnl.tblsft.com/sites/default/files/inline-images/Inline-607-monosemanticity-fig1-01-2560x896.png"
            alt="Anthropic neural feature map, from Anthropic research"
            style="width:100%;max-width:350px;display:block;margin:auto;"
          />
          <figcaption style="text-align:center;margin-top:0.5rem;font-size:.96rem;">
            <b>Anthropic neural feature map</b><br />
            <a
              href="https://www.anthropic.com/research/mapping-mind-language-model"
              style="color:var(--color-cyber-green)">Mapping the Mind of a Large Language Model</a
            ><br />
            <span style="font-size:.85em;color:var(--color-cyber-text-dim)"
              >Clustering a dictionary of neurons by monosemantic concepts</span
            >
          </figcaption>
        </figure>
      </div>

      <!-- 3. Animated agentic process (gif reference) -->
      <div class="showcase-item fade-in" tabindex="0" aria-label="Agentic workflow animated gif">
        <figure
          style="background:var(--color-cyber-bg);padding:1rem;border-radius:1rem;border:1px solid var(--color-cyber-border);"
        >
          <img
            src={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}/assets/images/QgFc9ovreXOjW8hVonunb.gif`}
            alt="Animated agentic workflow"
            loading="lazy"
            style="width:100%;max-width:350px;margin:auto;display:block;"
          />
          <figcaption style="text-align:center;margin-top:0.5rem;font-size:.96rem;">
            <b>Dynamická vizualizace agentního orchestru</b>
          </figcaption>
        </figure>
      </div>

      <!-- 4. Anthropic System Card Image (Claude 4) -->
      <div class="showcase-item fade-in" tabindex="0" aria-label="Claude 4 system card">
        <figure
          style="background:var(--color-cyber-bg);padding:1rem;border-radius:1rem;border:1px solid var(--color-cyber-border);"
        >
          <img
            src={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}/assets/images/claude4-system-card-img-008.png`}
            alt="Claude 4 system card visual"
            loading="lazy"
            style="width:100%;max-width:350px;margin:auto;display:block;"
          />
          <figcaption style="text-align:center;margin-top:0.5rem;font-size:.96rem;">
            <b>Claude 4 System Card</b><br />
            <span style="font-size:.85em;color:var(--color-cyber-text-dim)">Anthropic interpretability research</span>
          </figcaption>
        </figure>
      </div>

      <!-- 5. Extra: External - Agentic node diagram from Atlassian -->
      <div class="showcase-item fade-in" tabindex="0" aria-label="Agentic diagram Atlassian">
        <figure
          style="background:var(--color-cyber-bg);padding:1rem;border-radius:1rem;border:1px solid var(--color-cyber-border);"
        >
          <a
            href="https://www.atlassian.com/blog/artificial-intelligence/ai-agentic-workflows"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener"
          >
            <img
              src="https://i0.wp.com/www.atlassian.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Agentic-workflow-diagram.jpg"
              alt="Atlassian Agentic Workflow"
              style="width:100%;max-width:350px;margin:auto;display:block;"
            />
          </a>
          <figcaption style="text-align:center;margin-top:0.5rem;font-size:.96rem;">
            <b>Pattern: Parallel/Hierarchical Agentic Diagram</b><br />
            <a
              href="https://www.atlassian.com/blog/artificial-intelligence/ai-agentic-workflows"
              style="color:var(--color-cyber-green)">Atlassian: AI agentic workflows</a
            >
          </figcaption>
        </figure>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="learnmore-links" style="margin-top:2.5rem;text-align:center;">
      <h3 style="color:var(--color-cyber-green);margin-bottom:.5em;">Další čtení & zdroje</h3>
      <div style="display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:2rem;justify-content:center;font-size:1.08rem;">
        <a
          href="https://www.anthropic.com/research/mapping-mind-language-model"
          target="_blank"
          style="color:var(--color-cyber-blue)">Anthropic: Mapping the Mind</a
        >
        <a
          href="https://weaviate.io/blog/what-are-agentic-workflows"
          target="_blank"
          style="color:var(--color-cyber-blue)">What are Agentic Workflows?</a
        >
        <a
          href="https://www.knime.com/blog/why-visual-workflows-best-way-to-build-ai-agents"
          target="_blank"
          style="color:var(--color-cyber-blue)">Building AI Agents Visually</a
        >
        <a
          href="https://www.anthropic.com/news/core-views-on-ai-safety"
          target="_blank"
          style="color:var(--color-cyber-blue)">Anthropic: AI Safety</a
        >
        <a
          href="https://landing.ai/blog/visionagent-an-agentic-approach-for-complex-visual-reasoning"
          target="_blank"
          style="color:var(--color-cyber-blue)">VisionAgent</a
        >
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
<style>
  .showcasegrid > .showcase-item {
    transition:
      transform 0.22s cubic-bezier(0.6, 0.2, 0.6, 1),
      box-shadow 0.19s;
  }
  .showcasegrid > .showcase-item:focus,
  .showcasegrid > .showcase-item:hover {
    outline: 1.5px solid var(--color-cyber-green);
    z-index: 5;
    box-shadow:
      0 4px 24px 0 #39ff1455,
      0 1px 8px 0 #f8514940;
    background: var(--color-cyber-surface);
    transform: translateY(-2px) scale(1.022);
  }
</style>
